  Unfortunately, you’re about to find out how I almost ended up on a watch list trying to meet Olympic legend Michael Phelps, why I cried my eyes out in front of David Letterman as I sat next to disgraced politician Anthony Weiner and how I was injured so badly at Disney World that I had to pull a bocce ball-sized turd out of my own asshole just to have a chance at saving a family vacation. My hope is that this book can either save someone from going down the same destructive path with prescription painkillers that I did or that my Perc Era can at least make you laugh. Enjoy.


